{"id":2252,"date":"2024-07-13T21:42:24","date_gmt":"2024-07-13T21:42:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/yannichau.i234.me\/?p=2252"},"modified":"2025-08-14T21:38:29","modified_gmt":"2025-08-14T21:38:29","slug":"photopoems-4-a-sun-clouds-hills-and-a-bridge-of-thoughts","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/2024\/07\/13\/2252","title":{"rendered":"Photopoems 4: A sun, clouds, hills and a bridge of thoughts"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-1024x640.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2277\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-1024x640.webp 1024w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-300x188.webp 300w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-768x480.webp 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-1536x960.webp 1536w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/IMG_5406-2048x1280.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>The Sun<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like a timid introvert<br>Hiding behind the mountains<br>Gently peeking through the misty skirts<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Awake!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like drops of smearing paint<br>She blushes the entire canvas with tangerine streaks<br>Caressing the clouds with light medallion taints<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Rise!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like a brave, glowing flame<br>Her vibrancy came<br>Popping<br>Sizzling<br>Crackling<br>Frizzling<br>Filling the rifts with beaming scorching rays.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Rejoice!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Like an ephemeral thriller<br>Her magical glee vasnishes from sight<br>As she reveals the charming azure that stays.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1024x768.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2280\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1024x768.webp 1024w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-300x225.webp 300w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-768x576.webp 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1536x1153.webp 1536w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-2048x1537.webp 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>Clouds<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Caressing, gently, the<br>Lavish, immaculately white snow<br>On the<br>Utterly almighty Annapurnas, as I gaze upon it,<br>Dumbfounded and simply amazed!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-1024x683.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2237\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-1024x683.webp 1024w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-300x200.webp 300w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-768x512.webp 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3-1536x1024.webp 1536w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-3.webp 1897w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>Terraced Gardens<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Rows<br>alternating<br>highlights and<br>shadows gleaming<br>under the exuberant sun<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Jagged<br>and uneven<br>overloaded with<br>the benevolance of<br>farmers\u2019 tender footsteps<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">Steps<br>leading to<br>the azure blue<br>stpes descending<br>from what we call heaven<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large wp-duotone-grayscale\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"817\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-817x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2250\" srcset=\"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-817x1024.webp 817w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-239x300.webp 239w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-768x963.webp 768w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15-1225x1536.webp 1225w, http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-15.webp 1521w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 817px) 100vw, 817px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\"><strong>Bridge of thoughts<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">While I cross a cantilever bridge that<br>leaps<br>across the<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">deep<br>deep<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">valley<br>as I ponder upon my<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">deep<br>deep <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-dm-sans-font-family\">thoughts.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The Sun Like a timid introvertHiding behind the mountainsGently peeking through the misty skirts Awake! Like drops of smearing paintShe blushes the entire canvas with tangerine streaksCaressing the clouds with light medallion taints Rise! Like a brave, glowing flameHer vibrancy camePoppingSizzlingCracklingFrizzlingFilling the rifts with beaming scorching rays. Rejoice! Like an ephemeral thrillerHer magical glee vasnishes [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":2280,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[5,54,8,1],"tags":[61,60,17,51],"class_list":["post-2252","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-photography","category-photopoems","category-travel","category-uncategorized","tag-annapurna","tag-nepal","tag-photography","tag-photopoems"],"acf":[],"featured_media_src_url":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/image-17-1024x768.webp","_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2252","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2252"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"http:\/\/yanni-test-local-wp-newdb.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2252\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2284,"href":"http:\/\/yanni